  <header class="site-header" id="top">
    <h1>The Career of Malik Nabers</h1>

    <p class="lede">
      Malik Nabers (born July 28, 2003) is an American professional football wide receiver for the New York Giants of the
      <abbr title="National Football League">NFL</abbr>.
      He played college football for the LSU Tigers and is entering his second year with the Giants.
      He’s a <mark>volume-dominant</mark> receiver with <em>game-breaking</em> upside.
    </p>

    <!-- In-page Navigation Grid (rubric: navigation with links to areas) -->
